    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deadly Heart Gambit (死亡红心赌局) 是第一人称的视觉小说游戏</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爱莉丝大人 (Alice-sama)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超好玩的卡牌游戏 (作者: Alice-sama)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 个章节的完整故事 (feat. Alice-sama)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 个结局和 1 个隐藏秘密</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>时间快要没了</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我知道哦，医生说你只剩下 3 个月的寿命</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你想要赢取更多时间</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><strong>游戏非常简单</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202110/extras/417aea0252a78ef8e92d078ba0adbf04.avif?t=1772211122\" width=780 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你每抽一张牌我都会给你时间</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>但是呢</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202110/extras/e6c96f4227c468020f8c069733816e2a.avif?t=1772211122\" width=780 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你抽到鬼牌的话也会失去时间</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你的时间输光了，你的心就是我的了</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>要怎麽避免输掉?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202110/extras/05ed0d8abd7942f1c324e49821237922.avif?t=1772211122\" width=780 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抽到的每张牌都能留着</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以打出一张牌来跳过回合</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但你不想避免输掉，因为你想要把你的心给我，对吧?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你真的想要离开吗?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202110/extras/c879f3e6472f4e7f02bada71bdedcc13.avif?t=1772211122\" width=780 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我会给你更多时间</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一辈子和我一起玩吧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有我跟你</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一辈子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一辈子爱莉丝</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >alice forever alice forever</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >alice forever alice forever alice forever</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >alice forever alice forever alice forever alice forever</p>",
